"<application>MySQL</application> and <application>PHP5</application>. To "
"install Ruby base packages you can enter the following command in the "
"terminal prompt:"
msgstr ""
"若要运行 Ruby on Rails，您需要安装 <application>Ruby</application>、<application>Ruby "
"Gems</application>、<application>Ruby on "
"Rails</application>、<application>lighttpd</application>、<application>MySQL</a"
"pplication> 和 <application>PHP5</application>。要安装 Ruby 基本软件包，您可以在终端提示中输入以下命令："

