msgstr "DNS 指南"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1116(title) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:245(title) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:245(title)
msgid "CUPS - Print Server"
msgstr "CUPS － 打印服务器"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1117(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:246(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:246(para)
msgid ""
"The primary mechanism for Ubuntu printing and print services is the "
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">Common UNIX Printing System</emphasis> (CUPS). This "
"printing system is a freely available, portable printing layer which has "
"become the new standard for printing in most Linux distributions."
msgstr ""
"Ubuntu 印刷和打印服务的主要机制是 <emphasis role=\"bold\">CUPS</emphasis> (Common UNIX "
"Printing System，通用 UNIX 打印系统)。这个打印系统是一个免费可用的、可移植的打印虚拟层，并已成为大多数 Linux "
"发行版的新打印标准。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1124(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:253(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:253(para)
msgid ""
"CUPS manages print jobs and queues and provides network printing using the "
"standard Internet Printing Protocol (IPP), while offering support for a very "
"large range of printers, from dot-matrix to laser and many in between. CUPS "
"also supports PostScript Printer Description (PPD) and auto-detection of "
"network printers, and features a simple web-based configuration and "
"administration tool."
msgstr ""
"CUPS 管理打印作业和队列，并使用标准的 Internet 打印协议 (IPP) "
"提供网络打印，该协议提供最大范围的打印机支持，从点阵打印机到激光打印机以及位于两者之间的许多打印机。CUPS 也支持 PostScript "
"Printer Description (PPD) 和网络打印机的自动检测，以及提供基于 Web 的简单配置和管理工具。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1134(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:263(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:263(para)
msgid ""
"To install CUPS on your Ubuntu computer, simply use "
"<application>sudo</application> with the <application>apt-get</application> "
"command and give the packages to install as the first parameter. A complete "
"CUPS install has many package dependencies, but they may all be specified on "
"the same command line. Enter the following at a terminal prompt to install "
"CUPS:"
msgstr ""
"若想在您的 Ubuntu 计算机中安装 CUPS，只需通过 <application>sudo</application> 运行 "
"<application>apt-get</application> 命令并将要安装的包作为第一个参数即可。一个完整的 CUPS "
"安装有很多包依赖关系，但它们都可以在同一行上给出。在终端输入以下命令来安装 CUPS："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1139(command) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:268(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:268(command)
msgid "sudo apt-get install cupsys cupsys-client"
msgstr "sudo apt-get install cupsys cupsys-client"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1142(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:271(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:271(para)
msgid ""
"Upon authenticating with your user password, the packages should be "
"downloaded and installed without error. Upon the conclusion of installation, "
"the CUPS server will be started automatically. For troubleshooting purposes, "
"you can access CUPS server errors via the error log file at: "
"<filename>/var/log/cups/error_log</filename>. If the error log does not show "
"enough information to troubleshoot any problems you encounter, the verbosity "
"of the CUPS log can be increased by changing the <emphasis "
"role=\"bold\">LogLevel</emphasis> directive in the configuration file "
"(discussed below) to \"debug\" or even \"debug2\", which logs everything, "
"from the default of \"info\". If you make this change, remember to change it "
"back once you've solved your problem, to prevent the log file from becoming "
"overly large."
msgstr ""
"认证您的用户密码之后，这些包将被下载并正确安装。在安装结束之后，CUPS 服务器将自动开始。为了发现并修复问题，您可以通过错误日志文件 "
"<filename>/var/log/cups/error_log</filename> 来查看 CUPS "
"服务器的错误。如果错误日志并没有显示足够的用于找到和解决您所遇问题的信息，通过将配置文件 (下面要讨论) 中将<emphasis "
"role=\"bold\">LogLevel</emphasis> 语句从缺省的 \"info\" 改为 \"debug\" 甚至是记录每件事的 "
"\"debug2\"，以获得 CUPS 日志的详细信息。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1157(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:286(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:286(para)
msgid ""
"The Common UNIX Printing System server's behavior is configured through the "
"directives contained in the file <filename>/etc/cups/cupsd.conf</filename>. "
"The CUPS configuration file follows the same syntax as the primary "
"configuration file for the Apache HTTP server, so users familiar with "
"editing Apache's configuration file should feel at ease when editing the "
"CUPS configuration file. Some examples of settings you may wish to change "
"initially will be presented here."
msgstr ""
"可以通过 <filename>/etc/cups/cupsd.conf</filename> 文件中的指令来配置通用 UNIX "
"打印系统服务器的行为的。CUPS 配置文件与 Apache HTTP 服务器的主配置文件语法相同，因此熟悉编辑 Apache 配置文件的用户在编辑 "
"CUPS 配置文件时会感到相当容易。在这里将显示一些您可能想要改变初始值的设置范例。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1167(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:296(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:296(para)
msgid ""
"Prior to editing the configuration file, you should make a copy of the "
"original file and protect it from writing, so you will have the original "
"settings as a reference, and to reuse as necessary."
msgstr "在编辑配置文件之前，您应该将原始文件做个副本并将其写保护，以便您可以将原始文件作为参考并在必要时重用它。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1171(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:300(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:300(para)
msgid ""
"Copy the <filename>/etc/cups/cupsd.conf</filename> file and protect it from "
"writing with the following commands, issued at a terminal prompt:"
msgstr ""
"拷贝 <filename>/etc/cups/cupsd.conf</filename> 文件并对其写保护，可以在终端提示符后执行以下命令："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1177(command) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:306(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:306(command)
msgid "sudo cp /etc/cups/cupsd.conf /etc/cups/cupsd.conf.original"
msgstr "sudo cp /etc/cups/cupsd.conf /etc/cups/cupsd.conf.original"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1178(command) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:307(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:307(command)
msgid "sudo chmod a-w /etc/cups/cupsd.conf.original"
msgstr "sudo chmod a-w /etc/cups/cupsd.conf.original"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1183(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:312(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:312(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">ServerAdmin</emphasis>: To configure the email "
"address of the designated administrator of the CUPS server, simply edit the "
"<filename>/etc/cups/cupsd.conf</filename> configuration file with your "
"preferred text editor, and modify the <emphasis "
"role=\"italics\">ServerAdmin</emphasis> line accordingly. For example, if "
"you are the Administrator for the CUPS server, and your e-mail address is "
"'bjoy@somebigco.com', then you would modify the ServerAdmin line to appear "
"as such:"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">ServerAdmin</emphasis>：要配置指定 CUPS "
"服务器管理员的邮件地位，只需用你喜欢的文本编辑器简单编辑 <filename>/etc/cups/cupsd.conf</filename> "
"配置文件，并修改相应的 <emphasis role=\"italics\">ServerAdmin</emphasis> 行即可。举个例子，如果您是 "
"CUPS 服务器的管理员，并且您的邮件地址是'bjoy@somebigco.com'，那么您可以象下面这样修改 ServerAdmin 行："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1194(screen) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:323(screen) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:323(screen)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"ServerAdmin bjoy@somebigco.com\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"ServerAdmin bjoy@somebigco.com\n"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1200(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:329(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:329(para)
msgid ""
"For more examples of configuration directives in the CUPS server "
"configuration file, view the associated system manual page by entering the "
"following command at a terminal prompt:"
msgstr "关于 CUPS 服务器配置文件中配置语句的更多范例，通过在终端提示符后输入以下命令可以查阅相关的系统手册页："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1207(command) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:336(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:336(command)
msgid "man cupsd.conf"
msgstr "man cupsd.conf"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1211(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:340(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:340(para)
msgid ""
"Whenever you make changes to the <filename>/etc/cups/cupsd.conf</filename> "
"configuration file, you'll need to restart the CUPS server by typing the "
"following command at a terminal prompt:"
msgstr ""
"无论您在什么时间修改了 <filename>/etc/cups/cupsd.conf</filename> 配置文件，您都需要重启 CUPS "
"服务，在终端提示符后键入以下命令："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1217(command) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:346(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:346(command)
msgid "sudo /etc/init.d/cupsys restart"
msgstr "sudo /etc/init.d/cupsys restart"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1220(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:349(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:349(para)
msgid ""
"Some other configuration for the CUPS server is done in the file "
"<filename>/etc/cups/cups.d/ports.conf</filename>:"
msgstr ""
"CUPS 服务器的其它一些配置在文件 <filename>/etc/cups/cups.d/ports.conf</filename> 中："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1223(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">Listen</emphasis>: By default on Ubuntu, the CUPS "
"server installation listens only on the loopback interface at IP address "
"<emphasis>127.0.0.1</emphasis>. In order to instruct the CUPS server to "
"listen on an actual network adapter's IP address, you must specify either a "
"hostname, the IP address, or optionally, an IP address/port pairing via the "
"addition of a Listen directive. For example, if your CUPS server resides on "
"a local network at the IP address <emphasis "
"role=\"italics\">192.168.10.250</emphasis> and you'd like to make it "
"accessible to the other systems on this subnetwork, you would edit the "
"<filename>/etc/cups/cups.d/ports.conf</filename> and add a Listen directive, "
"as such:"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">Listen</emphasis>：在 Ubuntu 的缺省状态下，CUPS 服务器安装后只监听 IP "
"地址为 <emphasis>127.0.0.1</emphasis> 的环回接口。为了让 CUPS 服务器可以在网络适配器真正的 IP "
"地址上监听，您必须要么指定一个指定主机名、要么指定一个IP 地址，随您选择。可以通过 Listen 语句来添加一个 IP 地址/端口对。例如：如果您的 "
"CUPS 服务器在一个局域网中，其 IP 地址为 <emphasis "
"role=\"italics\">192.168.10.250</emphasis>，您想要该子网中的其它系统能够访问它，您可以编辑 "
"<filename>/etc/cups/cups.d/ports.conf</filename> 并如下所示添加一个 Listen 语句："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1237(screen) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:366(screen) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:366(screen)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"Listen 127.0.0.1:631           # existing loopback Listen\n"
"Listen /var/run/cups/cups.sock # existing socket Listen\n"
"Listen 192.168.10.250:631      # Listen on the LAN interface, Port 631 "
"(IPP)\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Listen 127.0.0.1:631 # existing loopback Listen\n"
"Listen /var/run/cups/cups.sock # existing socket Listen\n"
"Listen 192.168.10.250:631 # Listen on the LAN interface, Port 631 (IPP)\n"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1243(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:372(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:372(para)
msgid ""
"In the example above, you may comment out or remove the reference to the "
"Loopback address (127.0.0.1) if you do not wish <application>cupsd "
"</application> to listen on that interface, but would rather have it only "
"listen on the Ethernet interfaces of the Local Area Network (LAN). To enable "
"listening for all network interfaces for which a certain hostname is bound, "
"including the Loopback, you could create a Listen entry for the hostname "
"<emphasis>socrates</emphasis> as such:"
msgstr ""
"在上面的例子里，如果您不想 <application>cupsd </application> 监听环回地址 (127.0.0.1) "
"，您可能注释或删除了相关语句。但最好保留它以监听局域网 (LAN) 的以太网接口。为了能监听一个特定主机名所绑定的所有的网络接口，您可以为 "
"<emphasis>socrates</emphasis> 主机名创建一个 Listen 条目，如下所示："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1253(screen) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:382(screen) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:382(screen)
#, no-wrap
