#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1997(para)
msgid ""
"You can run PHP5 scripts from command line. to run PHP5 scripts from command "
"line you should install <application>php5-cgi</application> package. To "
"install <application>php5-cgi</application> you can enter the following "
"command in the terminal prompt: <screen>\n"
"<command>sudo apt-get install php5-cgi</command>\n"
"</screen>"
msgstr ""
"您可以从命令行运行 PHP5 脚本。若想从命令行运行 PHP5 脚本，您需要安装 <application>php5-cgi</application> "
"包。 您可以在终端输入如下命令来安装 <application>php5-cgi</application>：<screen>\n"
"<command>sudo apt-get install php5-cgi</command>\n"
"</screen>"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2027(para)
msgid ""
"Once you install PHP5, you can run PHP5 scripts from your web browser. If "
"you have installed <application>php5-cgi</application> package, you can run "
"PHP5 scripts from your command prompt."
