#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2625(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:18(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:18(para)
msgid ""
"Ubuntu provides two Database servers. They are: <placeholder-1/> They are "
"available in the main repository. This section explains how to install and "
"configure these database servers."
msgstr ""
"Ubuntu 提供两个数据库服务器。它们是：<placeholder-1/> 它们位于主软件库中。该部分内容说明如何安装和配置这些数据库服务器。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2641(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:34(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:34(para)
msgid ""
"MySQL is a fast, multi-threaded, multi-user, and robust SQL database server. "
"It is intended for mission-critical, heavy-load production systems as well "
"as for embedding into mass-deployed software."
msgstr "MySQL 是一个快速、多线程、多用户、强大的 SQL 数据库服务器。它旨在成为能用于大型应用、高负载的生产系统以及大规模部署的软件。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2650(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:43(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:43(para)
msgid "To install MySQL, run the following command from a terminal prompt:"
msgstr "要安装 MySQL，可以在终端提示符后运行下列命令："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2656(command) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:49(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:49(command)
msgid "sudo apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client"
msgstr "sudo apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2660(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:53(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:53(para)
msgid ""
"Once the installation is complete, the MySQL server should be started "
"automatically. You can run the following command from a terminal prompt to "
"check whether the MySQL server is running:"
msgstr "一旦安装完成，MySQL 服务器应该自动启动。您可以在终端提示符后运行以下命令来检查 MySQL 服务器是否正在运行："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2668(command) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:61(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:61(command)
msgid "sudo netstat -tap | grep mysql"
msgstr "sudo netstat -tap | grep mysql"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2677(programlisting) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:70(programlisting) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:70(programlisting)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"tcp        0      0 localhost.localdomain:mysql           *:* LISTEN -\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"tcp 0 0 localhost.localdomain:mysql *:* LISTEN -\n"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2680(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:73(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:73(para)
msgid ""
"If the server is not running correctly, you can type the following command "
"to start it:"
msgstr "如果服务器不能正常运行，您可以通过下列命令启动它："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2683(command) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:76(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:76(command)
msgid "sudo /etc/init.d/mysql restart"
msgstr "sudo /etc/init.d/mysql restart"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2690(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:83(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:83(para)
msgid ""
"By default, the administrator password is not set. Once you install MySQL, "
"the first thing you must do is to configure the MySQL administrator "
"password. To do this, run the following commands:"
msgstr ""
"缺省状态下，管理员密码是没有设置的。一旦您安装了 MySQL，您必须要做的第一件事就是配置 MySQL 的管理员密码。要做到这一点，可以运行以下命令："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2697(command) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:90(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:90(command)
msgid "sudo mysqladmin -u root password newrootsqlpassword"
msgstr "sudo mysqladmin -u root password newrootsqlpassword"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2702(command) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:95(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:95(command)
msgid "sudo mysqladmin -p -u root -h localhost password newrootsqlpassword"
msgstr "sudo mysqladmin -p -u root -h localhost password newrootsqlpassword"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2706(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:99(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:99(para)
msgid ""
"You can edit the <filename>/etc/mysql/my.cnf</filename> file to configure "
"the basic settings -- log file, port number, etc. Refer to "
"<filename>/etc/mysql/my.cnf</filename> file for more details."
msgstr ""
"您可以编辑 <filename>/etc/mysql/my.cnf</filename> 文件来进行基本设置 -- 日志文件、端口号等。详情请参考 "
"<filename>/etc/mysql/my.cnf</filename> 文件。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2715(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:108(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:108(para)
msgid ""
"PostgreSQL is an object-relational database system that has the features of "
"traditional commercial database systems with enhancements to be found in "
"next-generation DBMS systems."
msgstr "PostgreSQL 是一个面向对象的数据库系统，它有着传统商业数据库系统和下一代 DBMS 系统所增进的功能。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2722(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:115(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:115(para)
msgid ""
"To install PostgreSQL, run the following command in the command prompt:"
msgstr "要安装 PostgreSQL，可以在命令提示符后运行下列命令："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2729(command) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:122(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:122(command)
msgid "sudo apt-get install postgresql"
msgstr "sudo apt-get install postgresql"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2733(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:126(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:126(para)
msgid ""
"Once the installation is complete, you should configure the PostgreSQL "
"server based on your needs, although the default configuration is viable."
msgstr "一旦安装完成，您就要按您的需要配置 PostgreSQL 服务器，尽管缺省配置已经可以使它可以正常运行了。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2741(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:134(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:134(para)
msgid ""
"By default, connection via TCP/IP is disabled. PostgreSQL supports multiple "
"client authentication methods. By default, IDENT authentication method is "
"used. Please refer <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.postgresql.org/docs/8.1/static/admin.html\"> the PostgreSQL "
"Administrator's Guide</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"缺省状态下，通过 TCP/IP 的连接是被禁用的。PostgreSQL 支持多客户认证方式。其中 IDENT 认证方式被默认使用。请参考  <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.postgresql.org/docs/8.1/static/admin.html\">PostgreSQL "
"管理员指南</ulink>。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2748(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:141(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:141(para)
msgid ""
"The following discussion assumes that you wish to enable TCP/IP connections "
"and use the MD5 method for client authentication. PostgreSQL configuration "
"files are stored in the "
"<filename>/etc/postgresql/&lt;version&gt;/main</filename> directory. For "
"example, if you install PostgreSQL 7.4, the configuration files are stored "
"in the <filename>/etc/postgresql/7.4/main</filename> directory."
msgstr ""
"接下来的讨论假定您希望启用 TCP/IP 连接并对客户认证使用 MD5 模式。PostgreSQL 配置文件被保存在 "
"<filename>/etc/postgresql/&lt;version&gt;/main</filename> 目录中。例如，如果你安装 "
"PostgreSQL 7.4，该配置文件就被保存在 <filename>/etc/postgresql/7.4/main</filename> 目录。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2758(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:151(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:151(para)
msgid ""
"To configure <application>ident</application> authentication, add entries to "
"the <filename>/etc/postgresql/7.4/main/pg_ident.conf</filename> file."
msgstr ""
"要配置 <application>ident</application> 认证，请在 "
"<filename>/etc/postgresql/7.4/main/pg_ident.conf</filename> 文件中添加以下几条："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2765(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:158(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:158(para)
msgid ""
"To enable TCP/IP connections, edit the file "
"<filename>/etc/postgresql/7.4/main/postgresql.conf</filename>"
msgstr ""
"要启用 TCP/IP 连接，编辑文件 "
"<filename>/etc/postgresql/7.4/main/postgresql.conf</filename>。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2767(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:160(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:160(para)
msgid ""
"Locate the line <emphasis>#tcpip_socket = false</emphasis> and change it to "
"<emphasis>tcpip_socket = true</emphasis>. You may also edit all other "
"parameters, if you know what you are doing! For details, refer to the "
"configuration file or to the PostgreSQL documentation."
msgstr ""
"找到 <emphasis>#tcpip_socket = false</emphasis> 行并将其改为 <emphasis>tcpip_socket "
"= true</emphasis>。如果您知道您正在做什么，那么您也可以编辑其他所有参数。详情请参考配置文件或 PostgreSQL 文档。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2775(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:168(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:168(para)
msgid ""
"By default, the user credentials are not set for <emphasis>MD5</emphasis> "
"client authentication. So, first it is necessary to configure the PostgreSQL "
"server to use <emphasis>trust</emphasis> client authentication, connect to "
"the database, configure the password, and revert the configuration back to "
"use <emphasis>MD5</emphasis> client authentication. To enable "
"<emphasis>trust</emphasis> client authentication, edit the file "
"<filename>/etc/postgresql/7.4/main/pg_hba.conf</filename>"
msgstr ""
"缺省状态下，没有为 <emphasis>MD5</emphasis> 客户端认证设置用户证书。因此，首先必须将 PostgreSQL 服务器配置成使用 "
"<emphasis>trust</emphasis> 客户端认证，用以连接数据库。配置密码并将配置恢复成使用 "
"<emphasis>MD5</emphasis> 客户端认证。要启用 <emphasis>trust</emphasis> 客户端认证，可编辑文件 "
"<filename>/etc/postgresql/7.4/main/pg_hba.conf</filename>"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2785(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:178(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:178(para)
msgid ""
"Comment out all the existing lines which use <emphasis>ident</emphasis> and "
"<emphasis>MD5</emphasis> client authentication and add the following line:"
msgstr ""
"注释所有使用 <emphasis>ident</emphasis> 和 <emphasis>MD5</emphasis> 客户端认证的行并添加下列行："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2790(programlisting) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:183(programlisting) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:183(programlisting)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"local   all         postgres                          trust sameuser\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"local all postgres trust sameuser\n"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2794(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:187(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:187(para)
msgid "Then, run the following command to start the PostgreSQL server:"
msgstr "然后运行下列命令启动 PostgreSQL 服务器："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2799(command) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:192(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:192(command)
msgid "sudo /etc/init.d/postgresql start"
msgstr "sudo /etc/init.d/postgresql start"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2802(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:195(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:195(para)
msgid ""
"Once the PostgreSQL server is successfully started, run the following "
"command at a terminal prompt to connect to the default PostgreSQL template "
"database"
msgstr "一旦 PostgreSQL 服务器成功启动，在终端提示符后运行下面的命令以连接缺省的 PostgreSQL 模板数据库。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2807(command) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:200(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:200(command)
msgid "psql -U postgres -d template1"
msgstr "psql -U postgres -d template1"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2810(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:203(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:203(para)
msgid ""
"The above command connects to PostgreSQL database "
"<emphasis>template1</emphasis> as user <emphasis>postgres</emphasis>. Once "
"you connect to the PostgreSQL server, you will be at a SQL prompt. You can "
"run the following SQL command at the <application>psql</application> prompt "
"to configure the password for the user <emphasis "
"role=\"italics\">postgres</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"上面的命令是以用户 <emphasis>postgres</emphasis> 的身份连接 PostgreSQL 的 "
"<emphasis>template1</emphasis>  数据库。一旦您连到 PostgreSQL 服务器，您将会在 SQL 提示符下。您可以在 "
"<application>psql</application> 提示符中运行下列命令来为用户 <emphasis "
"role=\"italics\">postgres</emphasis> 配置密码。"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2820(command) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:213(command) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:213(command)
msgid ""
"template1=# ALTER USER postgres with encrypted password 'your_password';"
msgstr ""
"template1=# ALTER USER postgres with encrypted password 'your_password';"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2823(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:216(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:216(para)
msgid ""
"After configuring the password, edit the file "
"<filename>/etc/postgresql/7.4/main/pg_hba.conf</filename> to use "
"<emphasis>MD5</emphasis> authentication:"
msgstr ""
"在配置密码后，编辑文件 <filename>/etc/postgresql/7.4/main/pg_hba.conf</filename> 以使用 "
"<emphasis>MD5</emphasis> 认证："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2826(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:219(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:219(para)
msgid ""
"Comment the recently added <emphasis role=\"italics\">trust</emphasis> line "
"and add the following line:"
msgstr "注释掉最近添加的 <emphasis role=\"italics\">trust</emphasis> 行并添加下面行："

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2830(programlisting) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:223(programlisting) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:223(programlisting)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"local   all         postgres                          md5 sameuser\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"local all postgres md5 sameuser\n"

#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:2834(para) ../generic/server/C/databases.xml:227(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/databases.xml:227(para)
msgid ""
"The above configuration is not complete by any means. Please refer <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.postgresql.org/docs/8.1/static/admin.html\"> the PostgreSQL "
